../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN-HISTORY.md:1400:## run-008 — 2026-03-31T18:59:32Z
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN-HISTORY.md:1402:# Final Decision Memo - beyond-de-giorgi / run-008
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN-HISTORY.md:1413:Chain 01 remains the best floor-only screen, but its strongest likely output is mission infrastructure rather than the most distinctive next theorem-facing strike. Chain 02 remains valuable, but it is the most exposed to elegant repackaging and pressure/reconstruction collapse. The refined stochastic route is now disciplined enough that its downside is still useful, while its upside remains materially more original than the atlas route.
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/CHAIN-HISTORY.md:1419:The refined stochastic branch keeps a genuinely different structural reservoir: exact viscous-Lagrangian transport, circulation, backward-flow, and martingale observables. That is the highest novelty branch still on the board. At the same time, its refined version no longer mistakes exact representation for progress. It is now set up to fail usefully and early if the gain is only expectation-level, non-coercive, non-localizable, or solution-class fragile.
