../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/planner.md:10:- Tao's 2016 averaged-model filter remains mandatory, but not sufficient. A live chain must both name structure plausibly destroyed by averaging and show how that structure reaches one concrete endpoint or one useful obstruction.
../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-008/planner.md:18:Why it belongs now: several attractive branches have died because they reached the endpoint screen too late. This chain front-loads the shared admission work and should prevent further budget from being spent on Tao-compatible or already-collapsed structure.
