../../../../missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/judgments/chain-01.md:15:This is the load-bearing criticism. The original Step 1 speaks of what averaging preserves or destroys, but it does not force a single comparison level or a single observable. That leaves too much room for sliding between identity-level failure, transport failure, and actual bottleneck relevance.
