../../planning-runs/run-008/judgments/chain-03.md:79:- Expand the negative taxonomy to include expectation-only gain, parasitic framework import, and localization collapse.
../../planning-runs/run-008/judgments/chain-03.md:85:Most likely presentable result: a strong obstruction memo showing that the stochastic representation is exact but only expectation-level, non-coercive, solution-class fragile, or localized too weakly to constrain blowup.
