+
+- A branch can narrow honestly to one burden and one comparator neighborhood
+  without actually freezing a usable observable.
+- If the local record names only family labels and not one theorem-facing
+  observable with one sentence of leverage, keep the result at `menu-level
+  setup obstruction`.
