+# Meta Note - Step 012 Exploration 002
+
+- Naming one literature neighborhood is not the same as clearing prior-art.
+- Make the comparator burden mechanical:
+  one exact already-standard gain,
+  one exact claimed new gain,
+  or else stop the branch before formal identity work.
+- Anti-repackaging rules are strongest when written in the branch's own burden
+  currency:
+  expectation-only,
+  filtration-only,
+  localization-only,
+  or parasitic-framework-only consequences do not count.
